{"tid":1790911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度政府中斷新德里網路通信封鎖交通 三人以上屬非法集結過千人被捕穆斯林4女子零裝備阻防暴警打人 總理莫迪呼籲國民團結","createTime":"2019-12-20T10:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T20:19:55.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"63d84522b4963e0dbb5a5027e4ef0cd8fa8b22f3","tid":1790911,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/412143/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8D-%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%8F%8A%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F412143%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%258F%258D-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Y5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=3e3b27bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/412143/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8D-%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%8F%8A%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n印度反《公民身份法案》示威持續 網絡及集會活動受限制<br />\n<br />\n即時國際<br />\n<br />\n撰文：李福源<br />\n2019-12-20 06:00<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-12-20 06:00<br />\n印度反對《公民身份修正案》（Citizenship Amendment Bill，CAB）示威持續，首都新德里部分地區12月19日上午陸續出現網絡中斷狀況，另外警方亦限制集會活動，禁止3人以上的非法集結，並因此拘捕上千名示威者。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，印度當局為鎮壓示威而實施交通管制及封鎖道路，導致多個地方出現大規模交通擠塞，還下令關閉新德里部分地區的通訊服務，多間電信商的用戶均受到波及。<br />\n<br />\n印度電信商Airtel表示，受影響的區域包括塞倫布爾（Seelampur）、巴瓦納（Bawana）、賈夫巴德（Jaffarbad）等地，「我們將遵照政府相關部門的指示，暫停部分地區的語音、簡訊、網路數據服務；一旦相關指令取消，我們的服務將會全面恢復，很抱歉給您帶來不便。」<br />\n<br />\n印度歷史學家古哈（Ramachandra Guha）是其中一名被警方拘留的人，他接受英國廣播公司（BBC）訪問時表示，他與數百名來自不同背景的人均同樣被捕，「這清楚表明，事實上有很多印度人都反對這項充滿歧視的法案」。<br />\n<br />\n印度連日示威 穆斯林4女子「零裝備」阻防暴警打人<br />\n【新聞背後】印度長期排斥穆斯林政策 終釀大規模衝突<br />\n印度反《公民身份法案》示威規模擴大 莫迪Twitter推文籲團結"},{"pid":"9e9c9eb498b03d905d54b2410737e8ffcc6915ad","tid":1790911,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:53:40.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"902f572273016f04030eb4df7111efa573754820","tid":1790911,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11bcaed25f3b8cdb05e524d4d726134544eda1e","tid":1790911,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Y5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=14d92ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href